Creates a new empty vectors object. Needs to be added to an image using gimp_image_add_vectors.
HELP

    &pdb_misc;

    @inargs = ( &std_image_arg,
        { name => 'name', type => 'string',
          desc => 'the name of the new vector object.',
          init => 1 }
    );

